  "instructions": [
    "in a large bowl, whisk together coconut oil, brown sugar, eggs, flour, sea salt, and black pepper.",
    "add the ground pistachios to the bowl and mix until a sticky dough forms.",
    "cover the dough and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "divide the dough into 4 equal pieces and shape each piece into a ball.",
    "roll each ball between your hands to flatten slightly.",
    "heat a non-stick pan over medium heat and cook each pancake for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until golden brown.",
    "serve the pancakes in a stone bowl and top with shredded coconut and vanilla extract.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
